ActParliament of Canada Act
SubjectAppointment of the Honorable Pablo Rodriguez and the Honourable Bardish Chagger
PrecisOrder (1) Terminating the appointments made by Order in Council P.C. 2016-749 of August 22, 2016; and (2) Appointing the Honourable PABLO RODRIGUEZ and the Honourable BARDISH CHAGGER, members of the Queen’s Privy Council for Canada, to be members of the Board of Internal Economy of the House of Commons.
